docs {
  # TokenRelay Status

  Retrieves the current status of TokenRelay including:
  - Service uptime
  - Target configurations
  - Health check status for each target
  - OAuth cache statistics (if available)

  ## Expected Response
  ```json
  {
    "status": "healthy",
    "targets": {
      "oauth-test-api": {
        "enabled": true,
        "authType": "oauth",
        "health": "healthy"
      },
      "oauth-test-client-creds": {
        "enabled": true,
        "authType": "oauth",
        "health": "healthy"
      }
    },
    "uptime": "...",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  }
  ```
}
